--Acclaim has announced the release of RC Revenge Pro for the Sony PlayStation 2. 

Players can race their RC vehicles around twilight villages, across desert 

islands, and through lagoons and valleys. They can also assault opposing racers 

with a variety of weapons including water balloons, oil slicks, and lightening 

bolts. Additionally, the game includes a track editor that allows players to build 

their own courses and save their work on the PS2 memory card.
